               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the commissioner and his family members; a few lines in the incipit page of the text, alternating with black lines; two groups of lines alternating with black lines in fol. 9r; two initial lines of each section of the text; names of Hebrew letters in Ps. 118 (e.g., fols. 29vb, 33vb); elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; some other words, e.g., ṣällǝyu (e.g., fols. 14ra, 15rb), nǝbäl kwällǝnä (fols. 13va, 14rb), wäyǝbälu ḥǝzb (e.g., fols. 17rb, 18ra), wä-kaʿǝbä (e.g., fols. 30rb, 31vb), wä-tǝbl (e.g., fols. 32va, 33rb), wä-ʾǝmzǝ (fols. 36rb, 40ra).</rubric>
