- Chains of black and red dots as text dividers: fols. 8vb, 114rb, 120rb.&#xD;
- Writing exercises (Ethiopic syllabary) and doodles: fols. 1r, 2r-v.&#xD;
- Corrections written interlineally: e.g., fols. 9ra, 44rb, 61rb.&#xD;
